    "description": "<strong>特此声明: 麦斯历险记目前仅仅在Steam平台销售</strong><br><br>玩家交流QQ群: 706785876，欢迎大家的加入！<br><br>我们美丽的琳达小姐姐被强壮的Mr. Strong掳走了！为了救出她，我们的麦斯从此踏上了这场令人蛋疼的冒险之旅...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/4e81e99e9d99636ec9e67501b7497a28.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/4e81e99e9d99636ec9e67501b7497a28.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/4e81e99e9d99636ec9e67501b7497a28.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本游戏是一款无厘头风格的欢乐冒险游戏，特别适合把它推荐给想要整治的朋友，各路主播直播，或者自己娱乐自己。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/9fb7966f3c010734576d0435923a6b26.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/9fb7966f3c010734576d0435923a6b26.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/9fb7966f3c010734576d0435923a6b26.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/d9d1ec4cc0d9f5f9e357fc5a7b5c0d8d.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">很多关卡不能按照常理去思考，你要是规规矩矩的打那可是没办法通关的，一定要敢于想象，敢于尝试。 </ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/d8dac20e339e493c0dafb5e3c0b9ec8b.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">众多大家耳熟能详的欠揍面孔，配合游戏中的沙雕设计，建议保护好自己的键盘鼠标。 </ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/eb2d672c7835ac8cbc2183b3d865769f.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">除了不断向前的冒险模式，本作中随处可见其他类型的游戏元素，比如格斗对战，坦克大战，解谜，推箱子，飞行射击等等。当然，他们肯定也不会按照常理出牌，不然会很无聊。 </ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/a94b1f3db9f7a3b8cce752317e0936a2.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">本作可以通过特定的方块来互相切换2D和3D的模式，以及上下的重力方向，可以通过运用这些东西巧妙地通过一些看似无法通过的路障机关。 </ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/26904ed5ade9c886ee8e2c85302d8198.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/26904ed5ade9c886ee8e2c85302d8198.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/26904ed5ade9c886ee8e2c85302d8198.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/4b767cc3341d0b38cc52e508f4d9602a.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">在某些关卡中，你甚至需要重新定义游戏的规则，并且按照你自己定义的规则获取胜利。 </ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/7bca72e31345eecb21a20b69541b631c.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/7bca72e31345eecb21a20b69541b631c.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/7bca72e31345eecb21a20b69541b631c.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/8f0869c112e477af6305c7093b2468aa.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">死亡的花样繁多，有的还很震撼！ </ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/c37aaf8b1f4aae2843354914b0ad10be.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/c37aaf8b1f4aae2843354914b0ad10be.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/c37aaf8b1f4aae2843354914b0ad10be.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/2913195bfe35e3545be381fac61d2532.webp?t=1643182215\" width=625 height=50 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">由音乐制作人YuZiXi创作的独特逗比以及其他风格的原声音乐，给你一个非常好的游戏体验。</ul><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/8078cacc6ca2f6af1148c98821ff0afb.webp?t=1643182215\" width=15 height=15 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/79fea95dc5ef08cb936f7a1d6fdf6bc3.webp?t=1643182215\" width=7 height=15 /></span>👆想要了解更多一下？那就上滑好好看看宣传片吧！友情提示，请打开音量以增强观影体验👆</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/f9270d6a0dc418ba0662c92f6db78e9e.webp?t=1643182215\" width=67 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/39b1ca314cf2a05ecafb668cd4b47f00.poster.avif?t=1643182215\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/39b1ca314cf2a05ecafb668cd4b47f00.webm?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/39b1ca314cf2a05ecafb668cd4b47f00.mp4?t=1643182215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/8078cacc6ca2f6af1148c98821ff0afb.webp?t=1643182215\" width=15 height=15 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/8078cacc6ca2f6af1148c98821ff0afb.webp?t=1643182215\" width=15 height=15 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/8078cacc6ca2f6af1148c98821ff0afb.webp?t=1643182215\" width=15 height=15 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/8078cacc6ca2f6af1148c98821ff0afb.webp?t=1643182215\" width=15 height=15 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381530/extras/79fea95dc5ef08cb936f7a1d6fdf6bc3.webp?t=1643182215\" width=7 height=15 /></span>想玩的话那就别楞着了，加入购物车，打败强壮的Mr. Strong，救回小姐姐！</strong>",
